<h2>AI Marketing Challenges and Concerns</h2>
<p><strong>42. 40% of marketers cite data privacy as their top AI concern.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://coschedule.com/ai-marketing-statistics">CoSchedule</a>, 2025
Privacy regulations and customer data handling remain the biggest barrier to AI adoption.</p>
<p><strong>43. 38% lack the technical expertise to implement AI effectively.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://coschedule.com/ai-marketing-statistics">CoSchedule</a>, 2025
Only 17% of marketers using AI receive proper training. The skills gap is real.</p>
<p><strong>44. 33% see implementation costs as a barrier.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://coschedule.com/ai-marketing-statistics">CoSchedule</a>, 2025
